  <p>
    Few septic topics generate more questions — or more secondhand misinformation — than permits and
    approvals. The single most useful thing to know is where the questions belong: with the
    appropriate government authority, whose requirements are the ones that actually govern your
    property. This guide is orientation to help you ask the right questions in the right place, not a
    substitute for that authority.
  </p>

